BEGIN_PGML

a) What is [`f^{-1}([$fout1])`]? [____________]

a) What is [`f^{-1}\left(g^{-1}([$gout2])\right)`]? [____________]

a) What is [`f\left(g^{-1}([$gout3])\right)`]? [____________]

a) What is [`g\left(g^{-1}([$b])\right)`]? [____________]



END_PGML

